<article class="row hentry post-269090 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-news tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-domestic-workers tag-health-care-workers tag-nurses tag-osha tag-unions tag-workplace-protections section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-labor" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/coronavirus-will-spread-faster-because-we-lack-universal-health-care/" title="Coronavirus Will Spread Faster Because We Lack Universal Health Care">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0310-grand-princess-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Tents are set up at the dock a large cruise ship is docked at" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0310-grand-princess-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0310-grand-princess-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0310-grand-princess-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0310-grand-princess-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0310-grand-princess-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/op-ed/' rel='category' class='op-ed'>Op-Ed</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/coronavirus-will-spread-faster-because-we-lack-universal-health-care/">Coronavirus Will Spread Faster Because We Lack Universal Health Care</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Under the U.S.’s for-profit health system, the epidemic is not being treated like the public emergency it is.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/joel-segal/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Joel Segal</a></span> & </dd>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/harvey-wasserman/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Harvey Wasserman</a></span>, </dd>
